<br>
I think a transfer option would be a positive thing, personally. The community would not suffer (it wouldn't take long for the new characters to find their places) and it would give the folks who really want to be here a chance to come without losing their main characters (and a lot of time). I would definitely impose a limit on the number of folks allowed to transfer (and even a limit to the number from any particular guild). Even with that, there's just no way to do it without facing a ton of problems. Not to mention the fact that it wouldn't be fair to everyone who put time and effort into new characters on FV.<br>
<br>
Even with all the problems, I'd love to see a character transfer option here.<br>
